node.text:
All of our cases are hand made in Canada and this is how we do it:
-
Woods Used.
Back Ground: Wenge
Axes: Walnut
Sun: padauk
Wilderness Wording: Maple
Mountains: cherry
-
After all the pieces are cut, they are laid up on 2 way adhesive and pressed through a roller to secure each piece in place.
-
Then it’s time to press the assembled wooden back in to the protective shell.
-
Next up is a final clean and inspection before it’s packaged up and shipped out to you!
-
Shop this design and more at www.KeywayDesigns.com
-
#wilderness #wildernessnation #wildernessculture #veneer #wood #CanadianMade

We have been having a blast creating the new O&O series for you and we’re working hard to keep up with the demand! We’re fine tuning some of the processes that are slowing things down and every day we’re turning a new corner with efficiencies that will help us release new cases more regularly. Thank you for the support so far! Also thanks to @bearingeast for capturing some amazing photos of the O&O for us! 📸

#wood #woodandresin #resiniphone #woodiphone #oneofakind #oneandonly

node.text:
Wow, that took some work!! Introducing the ‘One & Only’ series.
-
The processes we’ve been working on to develop this style of case certainly didn’t happen overnight. There were some roadblocks, failed pieces, long nights, busted blades, and some decent setup costs, but we’re at a point where we are happy with the results and ready to go full-out!
-
This series is going to be very diverse in terms of colour, materials, and mixtures. Each piece comes from a one-of-a-kind block and because of the way they are produced, no two will ever be the same. We’re going to be playing around with a ton of different materials, not just wood, so be sure to stay tuned for future updates!
-
#wood #resin #epoxy #woodworking #handmade #madeincanada #phonecase
